James Smillie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Smillie 0 James Smillie is a Scottish and Australian actor and singer known for his roles in flm, stage and television productions and voice over and animation. Smillie was born in Glasgow, Scotland and emigrated to Australia before returning to the United Kingdom to appear in stage roles in London's West End. On television, he is probably best known internationally for his role as Dr. Dan Marshall in the lavish 1980s Australian series Return to Eden.
